2x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Ryan_Reynolds_Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/deadpool"><em>死</em></a>侍明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞恩·雷诺兹</a>透露，他正在重启 90 年代的热门动画片<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">《来自火星的摩托老鼠》</em> 。</p><p>该剧在 20 世纪 90 年代播出了三季，主角是三只小老鼠，他们保卫地球，对抗摧毁了它们家园火星的邪恶敌人。</p><p>雷诺兹将与他的制作公司 Maximum Effort 以及 Nacelle 共同制作重启版。</p><p>在一份声明中（来自<em><a class="body-link css-nu68ka et3p2gv0" href="https://deadline.com/2023/07/ryan-reynolds-biker-mice-from-mars-animated-series-nacelle-1235443667/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://deadline.com/2023/07/ryan-reynolds-biker-mice-from-mars-animated-series-nacelle-1235443667/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Deadline">Deadline</a></em> ），他说：“有些人知道我是一名摩托车爱好者，所以我们选择骑上<em>来自火星的 Biker Mice 是很自然的事情。</em></p><p> “Maximum Effort 和 Fubo 期待与 Nacelle 的朋友们一起为这款邪典经典注入新的色彩。” </p><figure id="attachment_3345029" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3345029" style="width: 1798px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3345029" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-08-at-14.24.24.jpg" alt="" width="1798" height="1134" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-08-at-14.24.24.jpg 1798w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-08-at-14.24.24-400x252.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-08-at-14.24.24-800x505.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-08-at-14.24.24-696x439.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Screenshot-2022-11-08-at-14.24.24-1392x878.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/u