ive-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/paul-simon-live-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-simon">保罗·西蒙</a>表示，他已经尝试与他的现场乐队一起练习，希望能够重返巡演。</p><p>这位传奇人物于 2018 年宣布退出巡演，并在距离他长大的地方仅几分钟路程 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-simon-emotional-farewell-fans-final-concert-2382659">的皇后区举行了他的最后一场音乐会</a>。</p><p>在最后一场演出中，西蒙暗示他对未来的“一次性”表演持“开放”态度，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-simon-makes-a-surprise-appearance-at-newport-folk-fest-3276105">于去年夏天出现在纽波特民谣音乐节上</a>，意外重返舞台。</p><p>现在，他向<em><a href="https://www.mojo4music.com/magazine/latest-issues/mojo-358-september-2023-siouxsie-sioux/">Mojo</a></em>讲述了自己的退休生活，以及他如何努力克服听力损失，从而阻止他重返巡演。</p><p>在讨论新音乐时，西蒙说：“我正在创作三首歌。其中一张已经完成。感觉就像是超越了《七篇诗篇》半步，演变成其他东西。</p><p> “这实际上是一个救星，因为我还不知道如何在听力损失的情况下进行表演，”他补充道。 “我尝试与巡演乐队中的成员一起排练，看看我是否能做到。到目前为止我还不能。这至少是音乐思考的一个出口。” </p><figure id="attachment_2382660" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2382660" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2382660" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Paul-Simon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2382660" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·西蒙.图片来源：Charlie Raven / Alamy Stock Photo</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-simon-announces-manchester-farewell-show-2236836" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">谈到他的告别巡演</a>，西蒙说：“我经常想知道，当我考虑自然结束我的表演生涯时，会是什么感觉。现在我知道了：感觉有点不安，有点令人兴奋，又有点松了口气。”</p><p>他补充道：“我热爱音乐创作，我的声音依然强劲，我的乐队是一支由才华横溢的音乐家组成的紧密、非凡的团队。我不断地思考音乐。我非常感谢自己的职业生涯很充实，当然，最重要的是感谢那些在他们的音乐中听到了触动心灵的东西的观众。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-simon-has-tried-to-practice-with-his-band-to-return-to-touring-3472146">保罗·西蒙 (Paul Simon) 试图与他的乐队一起练习以重返巡演的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
汤姆·克鲁斯表示，他的电影太空场景的拍摄工作仍在继续https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-says-work-is-continuing-on-his-movie-set-in-space-3472139?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tom-cruise-says-work-is-continuing-on-his-movie-set-in-spaceWill Richards Sun, 23 Jul 2023 10:24:33 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3472139 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="汤姆·克鲁斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他说：“我们一直在努力解决这个问题，我们会看看进展如何”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-says-work-is-continuing-on-his-movie-set-in-space-3472139">汤姆·克鲁斯 (Tom Cruise) 表示他的太空电影拍摄工作仍在继续，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="汤姆·克鲁斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/tom-cruise@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-cruise">汤姆·克鲁斯</a>确认他仍在计划制作一部在太空拍摄的电影。</p><p>这部开创性的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/edge-of-tomorrow-doug-liman-tom-cruise-elon-musk-nasa-space-movie-2676802">早在 2020 年就宣布了</a>，确认克鲁斯已与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克</a>和美国国家航空航天局 (NASA) 合作在外太空拍摄一部新电影，由<em>《明日边缘</em>》的道格·利曼执导。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-is-officially-going-to-space-for-his-next-movie-2758685">该项目原定于 2021 年前往外太空拍摄</a>，但最终被推迟。</p><p>尽管如此，克鲁斯坚称该项目的工作仍在继续，并且他仍打算制作这部电影。</p><p>在<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;"><a class="body-link css-nu68ka et3p2gv0" href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/mission-impossible-dead-reckoning-part-1-review-tom-cruise-3464795" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a44397944/mission-impossible-7-review-dead-reckoning/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One">《碟中谍6：航位推测第一部》</a></em>首映式上，当被问及影片的进展时，克鲁斯（通过<em><a class="body-link css-nu68ka et3p2gv0" href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/tom-cruise-space-movie-dead-reckoning-1235666807/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/tom-cruise-space-movie-dead-reckoning-1235666807/" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Variety">《综艺》杂志</a></em>）表示：“我们一直在努力工作，看看进展如何。” </p><figure id="attachment_3230706" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3230706" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3230706" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun.jpg" alt="汤姆·克鲁斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Tom-Cruise-Top-Gun-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3230706" class="wp-caption-text">汤姆·克鲁斯。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> NASA 通过<a href="https://twitter.com/JimBridenstine/status/1257752395750289409?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1257752395750289409&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fnews%2Ffilm%2Ftom-cruise-and-elon-musk-working-on-first-movie-shot-in-space-2659778" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter</a>证实了他们参与该项目，管理员吉姆·布里登斯廷 (Jim Bridenstine) 发推文称：“NASA 很高兴与 @TomCruise 合作在 @Space_Station 上拍摄一部影片！</p><p> “我们需要大众媒体来激励新一代工程师和科学家，使 @NASA 雄心勃勃的计划成为现实。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/more-details-emerge-about-tom-cruise-and-elon-musk-space-movie-2719148" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">这部尚未命名的电影通过克鲁斯、利曼、克里斯托弗·麦夸里和 PJ·范·桑德韦克的“热情的 Zoom 通话”向环球影业进行了推介</a>。</p><p>利曼正在撰写电影剧本，预计预算约为2亿美元。麦克夸里是<em>《碟中谍》</em>电影的编剧/导演，他将担任故事顾问和制片人，克鲁斯、利曼和范桑德韦克将担任制片人。</p><p>在其他地方，克鲁斯曾表示， <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-says-hell-still-be-making-mission-impossible-movies-when-hes-80-3465250">他计划在 80 岁时仍继续拍摄<em>《碟中谍》</em>电影</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_95 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_95" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-reveals-weirdest-rumour-about-himself-3466957"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> “<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harrison-ford">哈里森·福特</a>是一位传奇人物；我希望还能继续下去。我还有 20 年的时间才能赶上他，”克鲁斯在影片的澳大利亚首映式上告诉<em><a href="https://www.smh.com.au/culture/movies/tom-cruise-celebrates-birthday-at-australian-premiere-of-mission-impossible-20230703-p5dlch.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">《悉尼先驱晨报》</a></em> ，他指的是这位传奇演员在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/indiana-jones">《夺宝奇兵</a>：命运表盘》</em>中的角色。 “我希望继续制作<em>《碟中谍》</em>电影，直到我到了他这个年纪。”</p><p>此前，这位演员去年曾表示，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-says-he-doesnt-take-days-off-because-hes-living-the-dream-3230987">不会休息几天，因为他的职业生涯意味着他不断地“实现梦想”</a> 。 </p></div></div><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_tags tdi_96 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2" data-td-block-uid="tdi_96"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"></div></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tom-cruise-says-work-is-continuing-on-his-movie-set-in-space-3472139">汤姆·克鲁斯 (Tom Cruise) 表示他的太空电影拍摄工作仍在继续，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
